import React, {Component} from 'react';
import Team from '../../components/TeamCard/Team'
import Aline from './Aline.png'
import Ana from './Ana.png'
import Antonia from './Antonia.png'
import Arthur from './Arthur.png'
import Diego from './Diego.png'
import Gabriel from './Gabriel.png'

class Devs extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <section className="container-fluid p-0" style={{backgroundColor:"#009688", paddingTop:"4%", paddingBottom:"8%", color: "#fff"}}>
                <section className="container">
                    <section className="row">
                        <Team foto={Aline} nome="Aline Nascimento" funcao="Dev Back-end e Pesquisadora" />
                        <Team foto={Ana} nome="Ana Beatriz" funcao="Dev Fullstack e Social Media" />
                        <Team foto={Antonia} nome="Antonia Luciana Pires" funcao="Designer e Dev Fullstack"/>
                        <Team foto={Arthur} nome="Arthur Figueira" funcao="Dev Back-end e Negócios" />
                        <Team foto />
                        <Team />
                    </section>
                </section>
            </section>
        )
    }
}

export default Devs;
